msgid "List active forms for selector"
msgstr "Daftar formulir aktif untuk pemilih"

msgid ""
"Returns a list of all active forms for use in the Page Builder form element "
"selector.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Staff/Admin only\n"
"\n"
"        **Response includes:**\n"
"        - Form ID, slug, name, and title\n"
"        - Whether the form is multi-step\n"
"        - Field and step counts\n"
"        - URL to create new forms\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Mengembalikan daftar semua formulir aktif untuk digunakan dalam pemilih "
"elemen formulir Page Builder. **Otorisasi:** Hanya untuk Staff/Admin "
"**Respons mencakup:** - ID formulir, slug, nama, dan judul - Apakah formulir "
"multi-langkah - Jumlah bidang dan langkah - URL untuk membuat formulir baru\n"
"        "

msgid "List of active forms"
msgstr "Daftar formulir aktif"

msgid "Get form structure for rendering"
msgstr "Dapatkan struktur formulir untuk rendering"

msgid ""
"Retrieves the complete form structure including fields, steps, and "
"conditional rules\n"
"        for rendering on the frontend.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Public (AllowAny), unless form requires login\n"
"\n"
"        **Response includes:**\n"
"        - Form metadata (title, description, button text, messages)\n"
"        - All fields with validation rules and options\n"
"        - Steps data for multi-step forms\n"
"        - Conditional rules for dynamic field behavior\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Mengambil struktur formulir lengkap termasuk bidang, langkah, dan aturan "
"kondisional untuk rendering di frontend. **Otorisasi:** Umum (AllowAny), "
"kecuali formulir memerlukan login **Respons mencakup:** - Metadata formulir "
"(judul, deskripsi, teks tombol, pesan) - Semua bidang dengan aturan validasi "
"dan opsi - Data langkah untuk formulir multi-langkah - Aturan kondisional "
"untuk perilaku bidang dinamis\n"
"        "

msgid "Form slug identifier"
msgstr "Identifikasi slug formulir"

msgid "Form structure with fields, steps, and rules"
msgstr "Struktur formulir dengan bidang, langkah, dan aturan"

msgid "Authentication required (if form requires login)"
msgstr "Autentikasi diperlukan (jika formulir memerlukan login)"

msgid "Form not found or inactive"
msgstr "Formulir tidak ditemukan atau tidak aktif"

msgid "Submit form response"
msgstr "Kirim respons formulir"

msgid ""
"Submits a completed form response. Validates required fields and creates\n"
"        a form response record.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Public (AllowAny), unless form requires login\n"
"\n"
"        **Request body:** JSON object with field_name: value pairs matching "
"form fields\n"
"\n"
"        **Side effects:**\n"
"        - Creates FormResponse record\n"
"        - Records IP address, user agent, and referrer for analytics\n"
"        - Future: Triggers form actions (email notifications, webhooks)\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Mengirimkan respons formulir yang selesai. Memvalidasi bidang yang "
"diperlukan dan membuat catatan respons formulir. **Autentikasi:** Umum "
"(AllowAny), kecuali formulir memerlukan login **Badan permintaan:** Objek "
"JSON dengan pasangan field_name: nilai yang cocok dengan bidang formulir "
"**Efek samping:** - Membuat catatan FormResponse - Merekam alamat IP, user "
"agent, dan referrer untuk analitik - Masa depan: Memicu tindakan formulir "
"(notifikasi email, webhooks)\n"
"        "

msgid "Form submitted successfully with response ID"
msgstr "Formulir dikirim dengan sukses dengan ID respons"

msgid "Validation errors - required fields missing"
msgstr "Kesalahan validasi - bidang yang diperlukan hilang"

msgid "Save partial form response"
msgstr "Simpan respons formulir parsial"

msgid ""
"Saves a partial/draft form response for multi-step forms. Allows users to\n"
"        save progress and resume later.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Public (AllowAny)\n"
"\n"
"        **Request body:**\n"
"        - response_id (optional): Existing draft response ID to update\n"
"        - current_step: Current step number\n"
"        - data: Object with field values to save\n"
"\n"
"        **Behavior:**\n"
"        - If response_id provided: Updates existing draft\n"
"        - If no response_id: Creates new draft response\n"
"        - Only works if form has save_partial_responses enabled\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Menyimpan respons formulir parsial/draft untuk formulir multi-langkah. "
"Memungkinkan pengguna menyimpan kemajuan dan melanjutkan nanti. "
"**Autentikasi:** Umum (AllowAny) **Badan permintaan:** - response_id "
"(opsional): ID respons draft yang ada untuk diperbarui - current_step: Nomor "
"langkah saat ini - data: Objek dengan nilai bidang untuk disimpan **Perilaku:"
"** - Jika response_id disediakan: Memperbarui draft yang ada - Jika tidak "
"ada response_id: Membuat respons draft baru - Hanya berfungsi jika formulir "
"memiliki save_partial_responses diaktifkan\n"
"        "

msgid "Partial response saved with response ID and current step"
msgstr "Respons parsial disimpan dengan ID respons dan langkah saat ini"

msgid "Partial responses not enabled for this form"
msgstr "Respons parsial tidak diaktifkan untuk formulir ini"

msgid "Form or existing response not found"
msgstr "Formulir atau respons yang ada tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Upload file for form field"
msgstr "Unggah file untuk bidang formulir"

msgid ""
"Uploads a file for a file-type form field. Validates file size and type\n"
"        against field configuration.\n"
"\n"
"        **Authentication:** Public (AllowAny)\n"
"\n"
"        **Request (multipart/form-data):**\n"
"        - field_name: Name of the file field\n"
"        - file: The file to upload\n"
"\n"
"        **Validation:**\n"
"        - Checks file size against field's max_size_mb setting\n"
"        - Checks file extension against field's allowed_types list\n"
"        - Returns error if validation fails\n"
"\n"
"        **Response:**\n"
"        - file_path: Storage path of uploaded file\n"
"        - file_name: Original filename\n"
"        - file_size: File size in bytes\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Mengunggah file untuk bidang formulir jenis file. Memvalidasi ukuran dan "
"tipe file terhadap konfigurasi bidang. **Autentikasi:** Umum (AllowAny) "
"**Permintaan (multipart/form-data):** - field_name: Nama bidang file - file: "
"File yang akan diunggah **Validasi:** - Memeriksa ukuran file terhadap "
"pengaturan max_size_mb bidang - Memeriksa ekstensi file terhadap daftar "
"allowed_types bidang - Mengembalikan kesalahan jika validasi gagal **Respons:"
"** - file_path: Jalur penyimpanan file yang diunggah - file_name: Nama file "
"asli - file_size: Ukuran file dalam byte\n"
"        "

msgid "File uploaded successfully with path and metadata"
msgstr "File diunggah dengan sukses dengan jalur dan metadata"

msgid "Validation error - no file, invalid field, size/type exceeded"
msgstr ""
"Kesalahan validasi - tidak ada file, bidang tidak valid, ukuran/tipe "
"melebihi batas"

